The vial can sometimes turn negative items into positive ones, which was my most effective strategy. Be extremely careful with the ğŸ§« filter tool; in my experience, it consistently decreased item value or added 'botched' features. Avoid combining items that have already been processed by tools unless you have no other options, as this tends to make them 'overcomplicated' and negative.
